    </div>

    <div class="space-y-4">
      <div class="collapse collapse-plus bg-base-100">
        <input type="radio" name="faq-accordion" checked />
        <div class="collapse-title text-xl font-medium">What is OSR?</div>
        <div class="collapse-content">
          <p>
            OSR stands for "Old-School Renaissance" or "Old-School Revival".
            It's a style of tabletop RPG gaming that emphasizes exploration,
            player creativity, and challenge. OSR games typically feature high
            stakes, meaningful choices, and a focus on problem-solving.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

